data.title: An Epistle from Lady Jane Grey to Lord Guildford Dudley. Supposed to have been written in the Tower, a few days before they suffered. by (KEATE, George): (1762)
data.meta_description: 1st Edition - R. & J. Dodsley. 1762 - 1762 - Half title. viii, 19, [1]pp. 4to. Sewn as issued; a little torn at spine. ESTC T32811. The first edition of the author's second poem. Keate, 1729-1797, poet & writer, friend of Voltaire. - An Epistle from Lady Jane Grey to Lord Guildford Dudley. Supposed to have been written in the Tower, a few days before they suffered.
